igncenter size-full wp-image-1160" src="http://www.cyzerg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/mind.png" alt="mind" width="150" height="150" /></p><h4>Clear Your Mind</h4><p>Meditate and live purely; stay present, focused &amp; balanced. Shake your mind awake and watch it soar. [/one_thirdlast][/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_image="http://www.cyzerg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Careers2.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" alignment="center" background_layout="dark"][one_thirds]<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1162" src="http://www.cyzerg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/day.png" alt="day" width="150" height="150" /></p><h4>Day Trips</h4><p>Shift gears and explore adventures with your team. Fun stuff is part of everyoneâ€™s job description. [/one_thirds] [one_thirds]<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1163" src="http://www.cyzerg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/friend.png" alt="friend" width="150" height="150" /></p><h4>Furry Friends</h4><p>Our office is pet-friendly, so your furry friend is welcome to join you. (We love having them here, too!) [/one_thirds] [one_thirdlast]<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1164" src="http://www.cyzerg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/yaga.png" alt="yaga" width="150" height="150" /></p><h4>Working Yoga</h4><p>Need a breather? Relax! Recharge your body and re-energize your mind with free onsite Yoga classes.[/one_thirdlast][/et_pb_slide]

